What you need to know:

The board of the Heroes Council was only gazetted last month and is yet to be sworn in, making it impossible for it to perform its duties.Sources indicated that the board, chaired by Aden Wachu, will be sworn in this week by Chief Justice David Maraga.Some of those who were nominated this year include former Women Representative Zainabu Chidzuga from Kwale as well as long serving Standard journalist Munene Kamau from Kirinyaga